      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Safety Assessment: Is This Right for Me?</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Before engaging with a psychedelic substance, an honest and thorough assessment of your readiness — psychological, medical, relational, and contextual — is the most important thing you can do. This is not gatekeeping. Psychedelics amplify what is already present. Giving yourself the best possible conditions is not optional preparation — it is the practice.</p>
